{"tid":1621502,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［各區行動建議］出黎叫下行下 政府唔會驚","createTime":"2019-10-04T13:53:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T14:02:03.000Z","uid":199769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f66459af5237f12bbfc82fd729432f8d5a7b81fb","tid":1621502,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:53:33.000Z","msg":"行街叫口號有用的話，第一日已經成功。<br />\n<br />\n今晚警力異常真空，相信係等到午夜12點做野。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>兵貴神速，12點前必須盡能力施加最大壓力</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">行動建議</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">針對政府機關。</span></span><br />\n港島大家知邊到係春袋，萬事小心。<br />\n其餘各區，政府建築，大家明啦。<br />\n<br />\n唔建議狗屋，成效低，風險高，純浪費時間。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如冇政府機關可去參觀，先決定拜訪黑心企業。</span></span></strong><br />\n因為對政權直接採取行動，比拜訪黑心企業，目標及訴求更明確。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Anyway 尊重現場決定<br />\n天佑香港<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"411b37e2723908768ee245d1fbb4e230c8fd2ef3","tid":1621502,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:53:47.000Z","msg":"1:10"},{"pid":"b53c34b309416aa01a2ba557e0c523ce5313080e","tid":1621502,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:54:04.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"7719dc86d05e03202bcbec7e10272fc59c6ceb2a","tid":1621502,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:54:14.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"df92ce6ea0a432e310aef99210c8b4fe86d0e134","tid":1621502,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:54:49.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"69f2f667b3bdba88b7912ec66c93d4808fddfb3a","tid":1621502,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:55:01.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"de497a45f8cadcedde2ab43d5